---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CtaSection from '../components/CtaSection.astro';
import TestimonialsCarousel from '../components/TestimonialsCarousel.astro';

const schema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Service",
  "name": "Risk Planning",
  "description": "We help you prepare for the unexpected with a risk strategy that protects your income, your family, and your future.",
  "provider": {
    "@type": "FinancialService",
    "name": "Simple Wealth",
    "url": "https://simplewealth.co.za"
  },
  "areaServed": [
    { "@type": "Country", "name": "South Africa" },
    { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "KwaZulu-Natal" },
    { "@type": "City", "name": "Ballito" },
    { "@type": "City", "name": "Umhlali" }
  ],
  "serviceType": "Risk Planning"
};
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Risk Planning — Simple Wealth"
  description="We help you prepare for the unexpected with a risk strategy that protects your income, your family, and your future."
  activePage="risk-planning"
  showSocialInFooter={false}
  schema={schema}
>
  <section class="hero hero--short">
    <div class="hero__inner">
      <span class="service-hero-badge fade-up">Risk Planning</span>
      <h1 class="fade-up">Protect what you've worked so hard to build</h1>
      <p class="fade-up">Nobody likes thinking about what could go wrong. But having the right protection in place means your family's lifestyle doesn't depend on everything going right.</p>
      <div class="btn-group fade-up">
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn--primary">Book a free call</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section__header fade-up">
        <h2>Are you covered if life doesn't go to plan?</h2>
        <p>These are the concerns we hear most often.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cards-grid">
        <div class="card problem-card fade-up">
          <div class="card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M11 14h2a2 2 0 1 0 0-4h-3c-.6 0-1.1.2-1.4.6L3 16"/><path d="m7 20 1.6-1.4c.3-.4.8-.6 1.4-.6h4c1.1 0 2.1-.4 2.8-1.2l4.6-4.4a2 2 0 0 0-2.75-2.91l-4.2 3.9"/><path d="m2 15 6 6"/><path d="M19.5 8.5c.7-.7 1.5-1.6 1.5-2.7A2.73 2.73 0 0 0 16 4a2.78 2.78 0 0 0-5 1.8c0 1.2.8 2 1.5 2.8L16 12Z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Your family would struggle without your income</h3>
          <p>If something happened to you, would your loved ones be financially secure?</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card problem-card fade-up">
          <div class="card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect width="20" height="14" x="2" y="7" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M16 21V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>You have no backup if business income stops</h3>
          <p>As a business owner, your income is directly tied to your ability to work.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card problem-card fade-up">
          <div class="card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>You're worried about critical illness or disability</h3>
          <p>A serious illness can change everything. Proper protection means you can focus on recovery, not finances.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card problem-card fade-up">
          <div class="card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10"/><path d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3"/><path d="M12 17h.01"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>You're unsure what insurance you really need</h3>
          <p>With so many types of cover available, it's hard to know which policies are essential and which are unnecessary.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--grey">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section__header fade-up">
        <h2>Our approach to risk planning</h2>
        <p>We take a practical approach to protecting what matters most. Here's what that looks like.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cards-grid">
        <div class="card fade-up">
          <div class="card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="m21 21-4.3-4.3"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Find the gaps in your current cover</h3>
          <p>We review what you already have and spot what's missing, so there are no surprises when you need to claim.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card fade-up">
          <div class="card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>We work with expert partners</h3>
          <p>We partner with an independent brokerage to source the best cover for your situation, free from product provider bias.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card fade-up">
          <div class="card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M7 20h10"/><path d="M10 20c5.5-2.5.8-6.4 3-10"/><path d="M9.5 9.4c1.1.8 1.8 2.2 2.3 3.7-2 .4-3.5.4-4.8-.3-1.2-.6-2.3-1.9-3-4.2 2.8-.5 4.4 0 5.5.8z"/><path d="M14.1 6a7 7 0 0 0-1.1 4c1.9-.1 3.3-.6 4.3-1.4 1-1 1.6-2.3 1.7-4.6-2.7.1-4 1-4.9 2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Protection that grows with you</h3>
          <p>As your life changes, we adjust your cover to match your responsibilities without overcomplicating things.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card fade-up">
          <div class="card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Only what you need</h3>
          <p>We don't sell cover for the sake of it. Every recommendation we make has a clear purpose.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <TestimonialsCarousel grey={false} />

  <section class="section section--grey">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section__header fade-up">
        <h2>Questions you may have on our risk service</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-list fade-up">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">How do you decide what protection I need?<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg></button>
          <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer__inner"><p>We conduct a thorough review of your financial situation, dependants, lifestyle, and obligations. This helps us identify where you're most vulnerable and recommend only the cover that genuinely makes sense for your circumstances.</p></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">Will you review my existing cover?<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg></button>
          <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer__inner"><p>Absolutely. Many clients come to us with policies they've never reviewed. We'll assess what you already have, check for gaps or overlaps, and make sure your cover is still fit for purpose.</p></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">Are your recommendations fully independent and unbiased?<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg></button>
          <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer__inner"><p>Yes. We work with an independent brokerage that isn't tied to any product provider, so recommendations are based solely on what's best for you.</p></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">Do you handle the application and paperwork?<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg></button>
          <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer__inner"><p>Yes. Our brokerage partner handles the entire process from sourcing quotes to completing applications, so you don't have to.</p></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">How do you balance affordability with good protection?<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg></button>
          <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer__inner"><p>We work within your budget to prioritise the most critical risks first. It's about having the right cover in place, not the most.</p></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CtaSection />
</BaseLayout>
